Package edu.rpi.cs.csci4963.su20.dzm.pacman.game

Class Point

java.lang.Object
edu.rpi.cs.csci4963.su20.dzm.pacman.game.Point
public class Point
extends java.lang.Object
Helper class to hold and compare 2 integers. All fields and methods are public because this class should not be used for computation, just storage and comparison
Author:
Dylan Ross
